.TH "percpu_ref_switch_to_atomic_sync" 9 "percpu_ref_switch_to_atomic_sync" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
percpu_ref_switch_to_atomic_sync \- switch a percpu_ref to atomic mode
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" percpu_ref_switch_to_atomic_sync
.BI "(struct percpu_ref *ref "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ref" 12
percpu_ref to switch to atomic mode
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Schedule switching the ref to atomic mode, and wait for the
switch to complete.  Caller must ensure that no other thread
will switch back to percpu mode.
